    "uen": "202531026H",
    "description": "<p><strong>Pillarstone Pte Ltd</strong> is a Singapore-based contractor specializing in the provision of skilled manpower, RC (Reinforced Concrete) workers, and professional site supervision services for construction and engineering projects. We support a wide range of infrastructure, building, and maintenance works across both the public and private sectors.</p><p>With a strong understanding of project demands and regulatory requirements, Pillarstone Pte Ltd is committed to delivering reliable, qualified, and safety-oriented personnel to meet our clients’ operational and project needs.</p><h2>Our Services</h2><h3>1. Skilled Manpower Supply</h3><p>We provide a comprehensive range of skilled and semi-skilled manpower for construction and engineering works, including:</p><ul><li><p>Skilled Workers (all trades)</p></li><li><p>RC Workers (Rebar, Formwork, Concreting)</p></li><li><p>General Workers</p></li><li><p>Supervisors and Foremen</p></li><li><p>Safety Teams (Safety Coordinators, Safety Supervisors)</p></li></ul><p>Our manpower solutions support both short-term and long-term project requirements across public and private sector developments.</p><h3>2. Site Supervision & Professional Staff</h3><p>Pillarstone Pte Ltd supplies qualified site supervision and professional personnel for both <strong>part-time and full-time</strong> engagements, including:</p><ul><li><p>Resident Engineer (RE)</p></li><li><p>Resident Technical Officer (RTO)</p></li><li><p>PE Assignee</p></li></ul><p>Our supervision staff are experienced in managing site activities, ensuring regulatory compliance, and maintaining construction quality and safety standards.<br /><br />Industry Coverage</p><p>We supply manpower and supervision services for a wide range of sectors, including:</p><ul><li><p>Building Works</p></li><li><p>Foundation & Civil Engineering Works</p></li><li><p>Infrastructure & Transport Projects</p></li><li><p>Maintenance & Upgrading Works</p></li></ul>",
